article_id:2186,category_name:News,title_name:Adding the Mana Spiral to More Adventurers!,image_path:,message:<div>A sixth mana circle, the mana spiral, will be added to certain adventurer starting <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1620626400"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>The adventurer affected this time and her stats are described below.</div><div>Note: Unlocking an eligible adventurer&#39;s mana spiral requires special materials specific to that adventurer that can be earned from the daily bonus of the Trials of the Mighty quest.</div><div><br></div><div>■Affected Adventurers</div><div>5★ Gala Alex (shadow/sword)</div><div><br></div><div>■Stats</div><div><br></div><div>・5★ adventurer</div><div>
