				<span>Crisis Edge</span>
			</dt>
			<dd><div>Deals damage to the target, and reduces<br>their defense. After using this skill, or upon<br>using Umbral Erasure when the target has a<br>buff or is in break state, for a set period of<br>time it will be possible to trigger a "Skill Chain."<br>If Crisis Edge is activated during the<br>Skill Chain window, a variant with different<br>effects will be used instead, and it will deal<br>bonus damage if the attack connects.</div><div class="skill-detail">Damage: 202 × 3 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Special Effects:<br>・Defense -5%<br>　　Lasts 15 seconds<br>　　Does not stack<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain:</color><br>Damage: 202 × 3 hits<br>Damage: 485 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・110% against enemies with reduced defense<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain + Enemy is Buffed:</color><br>Damage: 202 × 3 hits<br>Damage: 495 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Special Effects:<br>・Dispels Buffs<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・104% against enemies with reduced defense<br><br><color=#00008B>During Skill Chain + Enemy is in Break State:</color><br>Damage: 245 × 3 hits<br>Damage: 668 × 1 hit<br>Skill Energy Required: 1,129<br>Damage Modifier:<br>・150% against enemies in break state<br></div></dd><dt
