<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a2241ae1de30904a24117f1388bd71782.png"></span><span>Liberated Assassin</span></dt><dd><div>Increases damage to enemies with reduced<br>defense by 30%. Also, grants Alex a strength<br>amp with a maximum team amp level of three<br>when she reduces enemy defense.<br>After this amp is granted, this ability will<br>not grant it again for 30 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/498b9ca4b18a9316d0fd08c5482745292.png"></span><span>Guardian Shadow III</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to blindness and paralysis<br>by 100%. When Alex is hit by an attack that<br>would have blinded or paralyzed her, her strength<br>is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/c53e9cf0657fced4c421ab241cc56d052.png"></span><span>Poisoned Punisher & Poison Edge I</span></dt><dd><div>Increases the chances of inflicting poison by 30%,<br>and increases damage to poisoned enemies by 30%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1620540000,update_time1620271268